<article class="card">
  <h3>JD7BOT Core — The Prime</h3>
  <p>Main interface of the JD7 system. Leads, activates, connects modules.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Security Bot — The Guardian</h3>
  <p>Anti-fraud logic, verification rules, protection of JD7 boundaries.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Navigation Bot — The Navigator</h3>
  <p>Routes, quick access, intelligent transitions between JD7 modules.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>System Bot — The Architect</h3>
  <p>Explains structure, metadata, system logic, JD7 architecture.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Shadow Bot — The Phantom</h3>
  <p>Hidden threat detection, shadow protection, silent monitoring.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Insight Bot — The Oracle</h3>
  <p>Recommendations, foresight, content analysis, guidance.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Motion Bot — The Runner</h3>
  <p>Clips, reels, dynamic content, motion-based actions.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Shield Bot — The Sentinel</h3>
  <p>Stability, strong warnings, red flags, system reinforcement.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Voice Bot — The Whisper</h3>
  <p>Social communication, text adaptation, messaging tone.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Pulse Bot — The Pulse</h3>
  <p>Music logic, rhythm, track identity, release integration.</p>
</article>